manufacturerProductDescription.media_text: Doll Travel Playset This Baby Doll Playset makes a wonderful gift for toddlers, girls, and children. Develop your child's imagination by introducing them to dolls so that they can learn how to properly interact with babies and role-play, nurture, love, and care for them. The clothing of the Doll can be easily changed, which helps young children develop fine motor skills. Set includes baby doll dressed in a onesie with matching hat and bib, doll carrier, doll bottle, doll pacifier, doll bib, and rattle toy.

Easy For Travel Kids love taking along this Strap and go easy to travel Doll Carrier and Car Seat wherever they go. It can be worn as a baby carrier or used as a car seat. Exciting entertainment in the backseat for long trips and a great alternative to screen time.

Baby Doll Size 12 Inch 12-inch doll Size is perfect for Kids of all ages to hold, hug, love, and enjoy for many years. Soft body is perfect for little girls to cuddle and play as well as for older girls who love playing pretend mom! It is compatible with most 12-inch dolls and accessories.

Angelic Face Doll has the most heart-capturing Cutest Face that shows warmth and love. Round cheeks and gorgeous eyes will make your daughter fall in love with her at first sight. The pacifier fits in the doll's mouth. Just like the real thing!

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect size baby doll for under 2 years.
reviews.reviewText: This is an adorable doll. Just the perfect size for an 18 month old to carry around. So many other dolls are so big and heavy. Added benefit is clip in the seat. Toddler can practice fine motor skills.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: My granddaughter loved the doll. It's her go to doll right now, but she's not into this type of carrier yet. She's two so maybe as she gets a little older she'll like it. She prefers to put the doll into a stroller or crib right now. The accessories are okay. I wish they were better made for toddlers. Their hands need to be able to hang onto them!!! All accessories that come with the product should fit.
